<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include("partials/head") %>
    <title>About Us | OrbitRush Tourism</title>
    <style>
      .about-hero {
        padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f3f8f0 0%, #fbfcf8 100%);
      }

      .about-grid,
      .values-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .about-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .about-visual {
        min-height: 500px;
        border-radius: 30px;
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 35, 20, 0.06), rgba(11, 35, 20, 0.22)),
          url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527631746610-bca00a040d60?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80")
            center/cover no-repeat;
      }

      .about-copy p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.85;
      }

      .values-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .value-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .value-card h3 {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .value-card p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .value-icon {
        width: 54px;
        height: 54px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: var(--primary-soft);
        color: var(--primary);
      }

      @media (max-width: 991px) {
        .about-grid,
        .values-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="page-shell">
    <%- include("partials/nav") %>

    <main>
      <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="section-kicker">About OrbitRush</span>
            <h1>Travel experiences presented with warmth, clarity, and trust.</h1>
            <p>
              OrbitRush Tourism is built around curated journeys, smoother planning,
              and reliable support. This page now matches the same green-and-gold
              brand language as the homepage and tour screens.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-space pt-3">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-copy">
              <span class="section-kicker">Our Story</span>
              <h2 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.6rem); line-height: 0.98; margin: 1rem 0;">
                We design journeys that feel special from the first page view.
              </h2>
              <p>
                From destination discovery to booking and enquiry, OrbitRush is
                focused on making travel planning feel exciting instead of
                overwhelming. The updated interface supports that goal with clearer
                hierarchy, more premium styling, and stronger consistency across the site.
              </p>
              <p>
                As your catalog grows, the same design system carries across new
                tours automatically, so the product keeps a polished look without
                redesigning each page again.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-visual panel-card"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-space pt-0">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="section-kicker">What We Value</span>
            <h2>Consistent presentation with a professional travel feel.</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="values-grid">
            <article class="panel-card value-card">
              <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-map"></i></div>
              <h3>Discovery</h3>
              <p>We make tours easier to browse and compare with cleaner sections and better visual rhythm.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="panel-card value-card">
              <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-heart"></i></div>
              <h3>Trust</h3>
              <p>The updated styling gives the brand a more established, reliable, and premium presentation.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="panel-card value-card">
              <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-headset"></i></div>
              <h3>Support</h3>
              <p>Calls to action, contact points, and booking paths remain familiar while the UI becomes more attractive.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %> <%- include("partials/scripts") %>
  </body>
</html>
